        <Summary>Play and download Youtube videos</Summary>
        <Description>SMTube allows to search, play and download Youtube videos. Videos are played back with a media player (by default SMPlayer) instead of a flash player, this allows better performance, particularly with HD content. SMTube also allows to download the videos, with the quality you choose. Several videos can be downloaded at a time.
	  
SMTube is included in SMPlayer's menus, to run it just select Youtube browser in the Options menu in the SMPlayer main window, or just press F11.</Description>
